def deprecated(func) 
56def deprecated(func):
57    """This is a decorator which can be used to mark functions
58    as deprecated. It will result in a warning being emitted
59    when the function is used."""
60    @functools.wraps(func)
61    def new_func(*args, **kwargs):
62        warnings.warn("Call to deprecated function {}.".format(func.__name__),
63                      category=DeprecationWarning,
64                      stacklevel=2)
65        return func(*args, **kwargs)
66
67    return new_func
